# Design tokens

**Inventory:** `docs/design/tokens.md`  
**Interaction contract:** `docs/specs/system/interaction-emphasis.md`  
**Canonical emission:** `client/src/index.css` (`:root` + `.dark`)

## Do not

- Add new CSS custom properties for one-off hovers (`--member-title-surface-*`, `--my-hover-bg`, ‚Ä¶)
- Use `hover:bg-primary` on graph / explorer / member chrome (periwinkle is for committed actions)
- Put brand gold on indexed token chips (use `--token-surface-{kind}`)
- Hardcode colors in JS/SVG attrs ‚Äî use `var(--token-edge-*)` / `var(--edge-*)` via `style`
- Hardcode `text-[Npx]` / `h-7` in components ‚Äî use scale tokens; run `npm run lint:tokens`

## Allowed sources

| Layer | Use for |
| ----- | ------- |
| `@theme inline` in `index.css` | Tailwind classes: `bg-muted`, `text-brand`, `border-brand-border`, `text-xs`, ‚Ä¶ |
| `:root` / `.dark` domain tokens | CSS `var(--‚Ä¶)` and `bg-[var(--‚Ä¶)]` when no bridge exists |
| `controlTokens.ts` | Interactive class bundles (`.hoverable`, `INTERACTIVE_ROW`, ‚Ä¶) |
| Component-local vars | Animation stagger only (e.g. `--shimmer-delay`) ‚Äî not theme colors |

## Semantic aliases (already in `index.css` ‚Äî reuse, don't duplicate)

`--interactive-toggle-*` ‚Üí `--surface-active*` ¬∑ `--member-sig-bg-out` ‚Üí `--surface-neutral-strong` ¬∑ `--file-chip-angular` ‚Üí `--file-chip-ts`

## Styling map

- **App chrome hover:** `.hoverable` ‚Üí `--brand` / `--brand-surface` / `--brand-border`
- **Token chips (body, sig, title pill):** `--token-surface-{kind}` in `tokens-chips.css`
- **Member row rest:** `bg-muted` on `.member-row`
- **Member header hover (chrome):** `--brand-surface` on `.member-row-header.hoverable`
- **Member title hover/trace:** `--member-row-trace-lit-bg` + `--member-row-trace-lit-border` on `.member-row` via `:has(.member-row-label‚Ä¶)` in `nodes.css`
- **Trace/Ctrl dim rows & sig pills:** `--trace-dim-surface`
- **Trace dim ink:** `--faint` / `--faint-ctrl` / `--faint-*` ‚Äî tune in `index.css`, no parallel dim tokens

## When strength is wrong

Adjust the **existing** token in `index.css` for **both** `:root` and `.dark`. If the same `color-mix` appears in multiple CSS files, consolidate to an existing named token in `index.css` (e.g. `--trace-dim-surface`) ‚Äî do not copy-paste mixes.

## CSS file ownership

`index.css` (emit + `.hoverable`) ¬∑ `tokens-chips.css` (chips) ¬∑ `trace-modes.css` (trace/Ctrl) ¬∑ `nodes.css` (member rows) ¬∑ `preview-wires.css` (wires/sockets)
